# Plans and planning documents

For this repository (`HOS_API`), **create all plans, roadmaps, and planning-style write-ups** (implementation plans, design notes, phased rollouts) as Markdown files under **`docs/`** at the repo root.

- Prefer descriptive filenames (e.g. `docs/FEATURE_X_PLAN.md`).
- Do not add new planning documents at the repository root; use `docs/` instead.
